your time and your space

08:02.000 --> 08:04.000
and everything 'cause you don't
have to answer to anybody.

08:04.000 --> 08:05.200
Nobody's gonna call you out.

08:05.200 --> 08:07.600
- Yeah...
but for the same reason

08:07.600 --> 08:09.400
that I shouldn't get a dog,

08:09.400 --> 08:11.100
I think that my life isn't

08:11.100 --> 08:13.367
conducive to
a serious relationship.

08:13.367 --> 08:15.233
Does that make sense?
- Yeah.

08:15.233 --> 08:17.166
- I mean, I'm not
a conventional person.

08:17.166 --> 08:19.367
I'll never--I don't think
I ever will be.

08:19.367 --> 08:20.767
I don't think you ever
thought I was going to be.

08:20.767 --> 08:22.433
[both chuckle]
- No.

08:22.433 --> 08:24.400
