keep my sh-- together?

09:11.467 --> 09:14.433
- What's going on?
- No idea.

09:14.433 --> 09:17.600
- I can't do it.

09:17.600 --> 09:20.266
(BLEEP)

09:22.333 --> 09:25.266
[sighs]
- You okay?

09:25.266 --> 09:26.734
- Yeah.
It's been a great weekend

09:26.734 --> 09:28.600
but let's end it
by telling you about

09:28.600 --> 09:31.166
my step-dad that died, and...

09:32.166 --> 09:34.433
I mean, I was eight years old,
you know.

09:34.433 --> 09:37.600
It's my mom having to,
like, deal with

09:37.600 --> 09:40.500
