09:40.500 --> 09:43.433
after we lost everything
because they weren't married.

09:43.433 --> 09:45.200
So we lost our house.

09:45.200 --> 09:49.433
I mean, we had nothing.
Nothing.

09:49.433 --> 09:51.100
[sighs]

09:51.100 --> 09:52.367
- I'm sorry, Chels.

09:52.367 --> 09:54.100
- We moved to, like,

09:54.100 --> 09:56.367
this duplex, really,
is what it was.

09:56.367 --> 09:59.767
My brother and I, like,
shared a twin bed, and...

09:59.767 --> 10:04.467
for life to change that fast
was just, like, mind-blowing.

10:04.467 --> 10:07.233
This is why
I struggle with, like,

10:07.233 --> 10:09.433
or why I guess I'm independent
because she, you know,

10:09.433 --> 10:11.633
she relied on him for so much.

10:11.633 --> 10:13.300
And like that [snaps fingers],
he was gone,

10:13.300 --> 10:14.734
and she had to work three jobs

10:14.734 --> 10:17.567
to, like,
put a roof over our head.

10:17.567 --> 10:20.367
I don't know if
my walls in relationships

10:20.367 --> 10:24.133
