always lived my life that way.

10:34.500 --> 10:36.266
I didn't think it was
gonna be this hard

10:36.266 --> 10:39.066
to, like, come back and...

10:39.066 --> 10:40.633
anyway.

10:40.633 --> 10:43.066
Moving along.
[soft chuckle]

